{"tid":2182733,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［胃］ 成日eurk胃氣+口臭","createTime":"2020-08-31T13:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T00:43:10.000Z","uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2e0abb33379b5fb2c9cc8d0dde20d2159300eec3","tid":2182733,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:21:34.000Z","msg":"半年前開始<br />\n朝早起身又eurk，每次起碼eurk 3 下<br />\n未食野又eurk<br />\n食完野又eurk<br />\n（冇食無定時，冇食過量/過少）<br />\n番緊工又eurk<br />\n除左eurk之外又冇胃痛果d<br />\n另外條女話我個口有陣酸縮味<br />\n就算刷完牙用完漱口水<br />\n條女都話都係聞到潄口水味夾雜住酸味<br />\n我去洗完牙 刷埋脷苔 都冇用<br />\n應該唔關牙/口腔事<br />\n令我懷疑係咪同果d胃氣有關<br />\n究竟我有冇咩test可以做下？<br />\n驗幽門螺旋菌有冇用？又唔想咁小事去照胃鏡...<br />\n定係中醫會有用<br />\n<br />\n求ching分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7ad4ab23891e229ae7b780f4bef51dadfd568f","tid":2182733,"uid":273006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:23:56.000Z","msg":"正餐之間有冇食零食？<br />\n我以前食好多，戒咗就冇呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23431759afd50847c59dd1781e185525eba4284d","tid":2182733,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af7ad4ab23891e229ae7b780f4bef51dadfd568f","tid":2182733,"uid":273006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:23:56.000Z","msg":"正餐之間有冇食零食？<br />\n我以前食好多，戒咗就冇呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:26:37.000Z","msg":"冇食零食，只有正餐<br />\n反而呢半年黎wfh食少左生果"},{"pid":"3fffcd15be8c8956b57a399a82cf383131ad17dd","tid":2182733,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af7ad4ab23891e229ae7b780f4bef51dadfd568f","tid":2182733,"uid":273006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:23:56.000Z","msg":"正餐之間有冇食零食？<br />\n我以前食好多，戒咗就冇呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T